32:50.642 --> 32:51.575
Yes, ma'am.

32:54.179 --> 32:56.981
Oh, and I take it you threw away
the rest of the brownies?

32:56.982 --> 32:59.884
Yes, ma'am.

33:01.253 --> 33:03.387
I really wanted that job.

33:03.388 --> 33:05.489
I know, and I'm really
