to the safety deposit box.

33:39.925 --> 33:42.326
If, you know...
Just in case.

33:45.430 --> 33:49.867
All right, then.
You sure
you don't want to go in?

33:51.937 --> 33:55.706
Yeah. I'm sure.
Yeah.

33:55.707 --> 34:01.612
Oh, and here.
This is-
This is for you.

34:01.613 --> 34:06.150
Go ahead. Take it.
Did wonders for me.

34:06.151 --> 34:08.385
How can you make jokes
at a time like this?

34:08.386 --> 34:13.724
I don't know.
Maybe it's because,

34:13.725 --> 34:18.395
for once, I'm not
thinking about myself.
I'm thinking about you.

34:18.396 --> 34:21.098
I'm gonna be thinking
about you every day...

34:21.099 --> 34:24.235
for a while, so...

34:25.637 --> 34:28.606
Well, you know
where to find me.

34:31.275 --> 34:33.577
I know where to find you.

34:35.781 --> 34:40.751
