34:50.762 --> 34:53.797
I'm gonna learn
to speak Vietnamese.

34:53.799 --> 34:56.132
You really should have
a goal when you're in there.

34:56.134 --> 35:00.671
You know, something to do.
Vietnamese.

35:02.874 --> 35:05.042
All right. I'm going.

35:09.314 --> 35:11.382
Bye.

